Sonicverse started from a simple frustration: too many workflows in the media industry were trapped in closed systems. We believe open standards and open code are the best way to accelerate innovation.

{% checklist title="How we work" eyebrow="Our Principles" %}

- Public roadmap and transparent decision logs
- Open source with MIT license
- A focus on interoperability and modularity
- Inclusive contribution pathways and community support

{% /checklist %}
